text: Phasmahyla is a genus of tree frogs. They are called shining leaf frogs in English. == Species == Binomial name and Author Common name Phasmahyla cochranae Chocolatefoot leaf frog Phasmahyla cruzi Phasmahyla exilis Mottled leaf frog Phasmahyla guttata Spotted leaf frog Phasmahyla jandaia Sazima's leaf frog Phasmahyla lisbella Phasmahyla spectabilis Phasmahyla timbo == Other websites == *. 2007.
